OL,3,CUK should sign climate change co-
OL,4,Coperation agreement with China, says
OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FThe UK should sign a formal agreement
OL,8,Fto co-operate with China on fighting
OL,9,Fclimate change despite tensions in
OL,10,Fother areas, a think tank has said.
OL,12,FResearchers at international affairs
OL,13,Fthink tank Chatham House urged
OL,14,Fministers to deepen climate co-
OL,15,Foperation with Beijing, saying the
OL,16,F"with us or against us" approach
OL,17,F"belongs in the Cold War".
