OL,3,CUK should sign climate change co-
OL,4,Coperation agreement with China, says
OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FThe visit is the latest example of
OL,8,FLabour's softer approach to Beijing
OL,9,Fafter a freezing of relations under
OL,10,Fformer prime minister Rishi Sunak,
OL,11,Falthough the Government has insisted
OL,12,Fit will "challenge" China where
OL,13,Fnecessary.
OL,15,FThe Chatham House paper suggested
OL,16,Fgreater co-operation on areas such as
OL,17,Femissions trading and carbon
OL,18,Fbudgeting, deploying low-carbon
OL,19,Ftechnologies and adapting to the risks
OL,20,Fposed by climate change.
