OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FJiangwen Guo, another of the co-
OL,8,Fauthors, said: "The UK and China have
OL,9,Fa long history of successful
OL,10,Fcollaboration on climate change.
OL,12,F"With rising geopolitical instability,
OL,13,Fand a retrenchment of climate
OL,14,Fleadership in some quarters, they have
OL,15,Fan opportunity to demonstrate the
OL,16,Fbenefits of bilateral co-operation,
OL,17,Fand in so doing shore up
OL,18,Fmultilateralism and accelerate
OL,19,Fpractical climate action, which is in
OL,20,Fall our interests."
