OL,7,FBut the authors also acknowledged the
OL,8,Fchallenges posed by the incoming
OL,9,FDonald Trump administration in
OL,10,FAmerica, saying the new president's
OL,11,Fharder line on China could pressure
OL,12,Fthe UK into abandoning co-operation in
OL,13,Fall areas.
OL,15,FThey said: "To be successful, any new
OL,16,Fphase of UK-China climate co-operation
OL,17,Fmust therefore account for these
OL,18,Fchallenges and be designed in such a
OL,19,Fway that it is resilient to the
OL,20,Finevitable political turbulence it
OL,21,Fwill encounter."
